data.name: GameTime_Warning
data.value: This game uses Time without Loads (Game Time) as the main timing method. LiveSplit is currently set to show Real Time (RTA). Would you like to set the timing method to Game Time?

data.name: Settings_Conversion
data.value: The autosplitter has been updated, would you like to have your settings converted?

data.name: Settings_Conversion_Completed
data.value:
The conversion process has completed. You may want to check your settings to make sure everything is still correct.
If you previously used the delay split option, you will need to manually setup Level Transition splits to achieve the same behavior.
If you previously used a mixture of manual and automatic splits you will need to manually reorder your split settings.
